node.text:
Watch now to see every look that made its debut at @Tavernonthegreen in Central Park during our #NYFW runway show, featuring a special musical performance by @arianadebose.
 
“I think we all crave romance and love of all kinds—love of your family, your friends, your neighbors, romantic love. This show is a celebration of all those things.” -xxMK
 
In that spirit, the company is proud to make a donation to @godslovenyc, an organization that is near and dear to Michael’s heart.
 
This production followed all NYC covid-safe protocols.
 
#MichaelKorsCollection #AllAccessKors

node.text:
From the iconic walls of Sardi’s on 44th Street, Broadway’s biggest stars come alive to celebrate Michael’s 40th anniversary runway show, which shines a light on NYC’s hard-hit theater industry. As a lifelong theater-lover, Michael is honored to use this occasion to show his support for the theater industry with a personal donation to @theactorsfund, which fosters stability and resiliency, and provides a safety net for performing arts and entertainment professionals over their lifespan. The Michael Kors company has also made a donation to the organization. #MK40 #MichaelKorsCollection #AllAccessKors

Featuring @bettemidler, @rosariodawson, @reneeelisegoldsberry, #JaneKrakowski, @alancummingsnaps, @suttonlenore, @judithlight, @kchenoweth, @sarabareilles, #ChitaRivera, @theebillyporter @arianadebose, @laurabenanti, @therealdebramessing, @mjrodriguez7, @cynthiaenixon, @marisatomei, @ashleyparklady, @mattbomer and @officialbernadettepeters.

node.text:
Our Fall/Winter show is all about the joy of getting dressed and stepping out for a night on the town. Filmed on location throughout NYC’s theater district, and featuring a performance by @RufusWainwright, Michael says, “this show is my fantasy night out.” #MK40 #MichaelKorsCollection #AllAccessKors
 
In support of the theater industry, Kors will be making a personal donation to @theactorsfund. The Michael Kors company will also be making a donation to The Fund.
 
This production followed all NYC covid-safe protocols.
 
Musical performance: @rufuswainwright
Film direction: @alexdebetak
Show design and production: @bureaubetak
Stylist: @mr_carlos_nazario
